00:01:45.760 --> 00:01:47.950
And thank you for asking.

00:01:47.950 --> 00:01:52.120
For me, conversation design
is a carefully curated

00:01:52.120 --> 00:01:56.410
back and forth between human
and artificially intelligent

00:01:56.410 --> 00:01:58.000
machine.

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:01.360
It generates a personalized and
context-sensitive experience

00:02:01.360 --> 00:02:03.880
around tasks and content.

00:02:03.880 --> 00:02:05.860
And it's content
that we experience

00:02:05.860 --> 00:02:08.440
in a very visceral way.

00:02:08.440 --> 00:02:11.320
It's like an immersive
experience filled with things

00:02:11.320 --> 00:02:15.760
that we can see, that we
can hear, that we can touch.

00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:18.310
