00:06:11.870 --> 00:06:13.430
I'm looking forward to it.

00:06:13.430 --> 00:06:15.810
Anyway, let's do a quick
thought experiment.

00:06:15.810 --> 00:06:18.230
Let's play, "how many
taps would it take?"

00:06:18.230 --> 00:06:19.370
All right.

00:06:19.370 --> 00:06:22.165
Simple equation--
what's 15 times 24?

00:06:22.165 --> 00:06:24.290
You don't have to take out
your phones or anything.

00:06:24.290 --> 00:06:25.289
But just think about it.

00:06:25.289 --> 00:06:27.384
If you took out
your mobile phone,

00:06:27.384 --> 00:06:28.550
how many taps would it take?

00:06:31.940 --> 00:06:32.950
You open your phone.

00:06:32.950 --> 00:06:34.080
You navigate to the app.

00:06:34.080 --> 00:06:34.910
You tap the app.

00:06:34.910 --> 00:06:38.430
You type the equation,
get your answer.

00:06:38.430 --> 00:06:42.510
I think I did it in eight
on my Pixel earlier today.

00:06:42.510 --> 00:06:44.040
Now how about this one--

00:06:44.040 --> 00:06:46.470
play the latest album by
Guerrilla's on Spotify,

00:06:46.470 --> 00:06:48.780
one of my favorites.

00:06:48.780 --> 00:06:52.340
I think on my device
I did it in 12 taps.

00:06:52.340 --> 00:06:54.090
I think there are a
